FILECOPY_1_FILE_OPERATION "$(FILECOPY_OUT_FILE_OPERATION_FILECOPY_1)"
GUI LOOKUP_CHOICE FILECOPY_OUT_FILE_OPERATION_FILECOPY_1 Copy,COPY%Move,MOVE%Delete,DELETE File Operation:
# =====================================================================
# The following GUI line prompts for the copy source folder flag.
# The default is YES.
# Possible values are YES or NO.
# Any value other than NO or no is interpreted as YES.
